# Agent request routing (daily-magic harness)

## First step on every request

Before planning or editing, scan **`.cursor/harness/agent-request-routing.md`**:

1. Match the user message against the **Routing table**.
2. **If a row matches:** attach the listed **`@.cursor/commands/<command>.md`** playbook.
3. **If no row matches:** continue with normal project rules and skills.

## Out of scope

Do not route to removed EnergyCenter agents (Bitbucket PR review, Jira delivery, Sentry incident, hybrid RAG). This repo uses Next.js + Neon + Tailwind, not React Router / SCSS modules / `enrg-frontend-styleguide`.

